This paper is about Central Auditory Processing Disorder, or CAPD. We will look at the definition, diagnosis, and how a teacher can help a student with CAPD in a classroom.

First, let us look at what CAPD is. CAPD is a problem with how the brain uses the information we hear. It is not a problem with hearing itself, but with how our brain understands what we hear. People with CAPD can hear sounds, but they have trouble understanding them. They may have trouble hearing in noisy places or understanding what people say when there is background noise.

The idea of CAPD was first talked about in the 1950s as "auditory imperception". Researchers were looking at children with communication problems. They started testing children in 1954, and in 1961, they developed a way to test how people hear sounds at the same time.

CAPD can make it hard for people to do many things. They may have trouble finding where a sound is coming from, or understanding two sounds happening at the same time. They may have trouble recognizing patterns or understanding changes in voice. Sometimes, one sound can block out another sound. They may also have trouble putting together clues they hear to understand what is happening.

To diagnose CAPD, doctors and other experts use tests. They watch how people react to sounds and use special tests to see how well they can hear. These tests may ask people to do things like listen to many sounds and choose the right one. There is no one test that works well for everyone, and we do not know what causes CAPD.

Teachers can help students with CAPD in a classroom. They can help by giving them extra time to listen and pay attention. They can also help by reducing background noise and using visual aids to help the student understand what is being said. This can help the student learn and succeed in school.

The play Twelfth Night says that disguise can be useful for tricking people. But it can also cause big problems. If you hide who you are, you may lose yourself. The play says you must choose between saving yourself or the relationships you have with others.

The play is about gender role reversal. This means men and women change places. This is a problem because it raises many questions. Why do people want to change their roles? In the play, a woman named Viola wants to be a man to protect herself. She is afraid of being hurt. Viola's plan works, but it also hurts her relationships with other women.

Viola is so good at acting like a man that a woman named Olivia falls in love with her. Olivia thinks Viola is a man named Sebastian. Viola also has feelings for a man named Orsino. But Orsino does not love Viola. He thinks she is a boy named Cesario. This is confusing and difficult for Viola.

The play may show that hiding who you are can help you understand your true feelings. Olivia and Orsino may have feelings they are hiding. But the play is not sure if this is true. It may be a way to make fun of people who judge others based on how they look. This is because Olivia easily falls in love with one man and then another. She seems to care more about her friends than her romantic feelings.

The play ends with Viola's true identity being discovered. Olivia says to Viola, "You are my sister." This means Olivia accepts Viola as a person and not as a man or a boy. The play says that being true to yourself is important, even if it is hard.

Many people note that German rule was very cruel, especially in German South West Africa. The German government killed many Ovaherero and Nama people. But this is not all that happened in the German colonies. The German colonies were different from each other in many ways. The German government spent more money on education in some places than in others. In East Africa, the British found many educated Africans when they took over in 1919. German education in Kamerun and other colonies was also good. 

But in South West Africa, the story was different. The government did not help much with African education. Missionary groups did most of the work, but they did not have much money. The government, however, spent a lot on education for Europeans in South West Africa. This had a big effect on the colony even after German rule ended. In South West Africa, many people were still uneducated and illiterate. Other German colonies had many well-educated Africans. What made South West Africa different? This paper looks at the reasons why. It also looks at how German settlers and government officials thought about African people.

There is a lot of writing about education in the German colonies. Most of these writings were in German and were written long ago. They mostly described the education systems in different colonies. Later, some people wrote about the differences between the colonies and how education worked in each one. One writer, Cohen, compared education in South West Africa and East Africa. He said the number of European settlers in South West Africa was a big reason for the differences in education there.

South West Africa was a good place for Europeans to live, with a mild climate and not too much desert. This is why many Europeans lived there. By 1913, 15,000 Europeans lived in South West Africa. In other parts of the German colonies, like East Africa, there were only 5,300 Europeans.

Heavy Metal music has changed much over the last 100 years. Today, it is hard to list all the different types of music that fall under this name. Many of these types, like rock, country, and jazz, have their own smaller groups, or sub-types. Heavy Metal is a special kind of music that started 40 years ago. It is expressive and diverse. It shows a wide range of feelings, mostly sad or unhappy ones. People who make this music like to experiment and try new things. This has led to many new types of Metal music.

It is difficult to say what is really Heavy Metal today. This music has taken ideas from other kinds of music, but it started from somewhere. To understand Metal music, we need to know what it is and why it exists as a movement.

Metal music is often about darkness. It is a type of music that is louder, more violent, and more exciting. People who make Metal music are good at playing their instruments. Metal music often comes from people who have taken drugs. In the 1970s, people used drugs and made music that was strange and new. This music was about the darker side of life. Later, people who made Metal music took inspiration from old music that was also about darkness. Some songs express this dark feeling, like the song "Helter Skelter" by the Beatles. This song was one of the first Heavy Metal songs and shows how music can be both sad and exciting.

Henri Rousseau was an artist. Before the Surrealist artists painted dreamlike works, he was making his own dreams come true. His painting, The Dream, created in 1910, shows a woman who is in awe of the beautiful things she sees in a dream. It also shows Rousseau's own dreams and goals as an artist.

Rousseau wanted to be accepted by other artists and art lovers. But he had a problem. He wanted to be different and original, but he also wanted to be accepted by the art world. This was a big decision for him. He had to choose between being different and being accepted.

To understand Rousseau's painting, The Dream, we need to know a little about his life. He was born in 1844 in a town in northwest France. His father was a tinsmith. He did not go to art school, but he worked as a customs inspector. When his first wife died, he had a lot of sadness. He started painting to feel better.

Rousseau wanted to be a famous artist, but he did not start painting until he was an old man. Many other artists were already famous when he began. But he did not give up. He kept painting and finally got the recognition he wanted.

The art writer Jan Gordon said that Rousseau and another famous artist, Matisse, were different. Matisse did not want to paint in a simple way. Rousseau wanted to paint in a way that was simple and traditional so that people would accept him as an artist.

Many smart people have said that there is a strong link between what is right and what is beautiful. I agree with them. Our brains immediately know that something is right or wrong, and we also know what is beautiful or ugly. One reason for this is because we do not learn these things from education or experience alone. We just naturally understand them. Our studies of right and wrong, and of beauty, are attempts to explain why something is right or beautiful, not to make rules for what is right or beautiful.

Critics of art or morals cannot fully explain what is good or beautiful. Talking about why the Mona Lisa is a great painting may include words like "light" and "color," but these do not explain why it is great. When we talk about our favorite book or painting, we often say there is "something" about it that is special. I think that both art and morals have this "something" that we cannot fully explain. This "something" is the most powerful part of art and morality.

We experience both right and wrong, and beauty and ugliness, at a deep level. This is something we can feel, but not fully explain. This connection between right and wrong, and beauty and ugliness, is stronger in literature. Literature is special because it has a moral message. It teaches us values that are important for living.

Germany is a strong country today. It has a unique culture. This culture can be seen from the mountains in the south to the sea in the north. It can be felt from the city of Munich on the Alps to the city of Kiel on the Baltic Sea. It can also be seen in the city of Cologne on the Rhine River to the city of Dresden on the Elbe River.

Germany was not always a strong country. The country has a history. Many people from different tribes created Germany. These tribes had their own culture. 

The name "Germany" comes from the word "Germania." This word has a disputed origin. Some people think it came from a tribe called the Tungrians. Others think it came from the word "ger," which means spear. Another idea is that it came from the word "garim," which means to shout. This could mean the Germans were loud.

A long time ago, a Roman historian named Tacitus wrote about Germany. He said the Germans were not mixed with other people. They were a group of people who lived in a wild country with bad weather. Why would people leave their homes to come to Germany? Tacitus said people would not leave their homes to come to Germany. Instead, the Romans would go to Germany to get goods and to fight in wars.

The Germanic tribes lived near the Roman Empire. They traded with the Romans and joined the Roman army. This helped the Germans grow and become stronger.

I looked down.  My mind was empty.  I was seeing something, but I was not thinking about it.  I was just looking.  A long time ago, I got some advice from an artist.  He told me to buy a book about drawing.  The book is called "The New Drawing on the Right Side of the Brain."  It teaches you how to draw.  One thing it teaches is to put a square around a picture you want to draw.  This helps you see the picture better.

I tried to do that, but I could not.  I was seeing too much.  A bowl of fruit was in front of me.  It was on a table in a kitchen.  I could not see just the bowl.  I was seeing too many things at the same time.

I remembered that some famous artists liked certain colors.  Picasso liked blue.  Monet liked green.  People from a long time ago liked many colors.  I was thinking that I could be an artist like them.  I was looking at the beginning of my picture.  I was looking at the start of my story.

I picked up a pencil.  I wanted to start drawing.  My hand moved over the paper.  Water was calm and peaceful in my mind.  Then, my hand hit the handle of the toilet.  A piece of poop was stuck.  It would not go away.  I was trying to get it out.  I gripped the mop tightly and looked at the poop.  It was a brown, messy thing.  I was not happy about it.

I waited a few minutes.  Then, I touched the toilet paper.  I wrapped it around my hand.  It felt like an oven mitt.  I bent down and put my hand into the toilet.  I was trying to get the poop out.

Teenagers are dying while driving. Several factors cause this problem. The National Institutes of Health say one reason is that the teen brain is not ready for driving. Driving is a big responsibility. Most teenagers do not have enough experience. This makes them more likely to have accidents, including rollover accidents, speeding, and driving off the road.

Teenagers also have more accidents when they drive with friends. This is a big problem. The Southern California Injury Prevention Research Center studied this. They found that the age of the passenger can cause more traffic accidents.

To make driving safer for teenagers, some states require a temporary license. This license limits the hours teenagers can drive and does not allow other minors as passengers. But these licenses are only temporary fixes.

The real problem is that most teenagers are not ready to drive. Psychologist Marvin Zuckerman says 18 is too young for a regular driver's license. He did research that shows many young people like to take risks. This is why we should delay driving until they are older. If we continue to give driver's licenses to young teenagers, many more accidents will happen. Many more teenagers will die.

We can make laws to solve this problem. Schools can teach driving classes, but no one under 18 can drive. A temporary permit can still be given before a full license. Teenagers must also practice driving with an adult. The number of practice hours can be the same as in most states. This will make driving safer for all teenagers in the country.

My idea is not new. It is a simple way to make driving safer for our teenagers.

I looked at films from the Library of Congress. They had many old Edison films. I watched all the trick films from 1895 to 1901. These films use editing to create illusions. My study was about the trick films. I looked at most of them and some of the later ones. 

Most trick films from this time are set in one place. They follow the rules of a play. The camera does not move. The shots are long or medium. This way is like a play or a magic show. The actors do not walk towards or away from the camera. They move side to side. 

One film is Uncle Josh in a Spooky Hotel (1900). The actors come in and move back and forth. They go out of the frame, but the camera does not follow. Most trick films have long shots and some medium shots. Close-up shots are never used. This is because in a play or magic show, the audience sees everything at the same time. 

Most trick films take only one shot to make. This is why they are short. They usually show tricks like magic, disappearing, or switching acts. However, sometimes one shot can be many pictures joined together. This creates the illusion of something happening. 

I looked at The Execution of Mary, Queen of Scots (1895). It is a trick film. When you look closely, you can see where the physical shot starts, even though it looks like one shot.

John Taylor was a strong supporter of Republicanism.  He was a farmer, but his farming work and short time in politics made him known for his strong opinions about freedom and government.  He wanted to protect and promote farming, the best job of all, in his ideas about government.  Taylor's belief in farming led him to think about many things, including how the government should be run.

Taylor thought the United States had a good chance to create a perfect system of government.  This was because the country had no old traditions to follow, so the people who created the government could make their own rules.  Taylor believed in the natural rights of people.  He thought these rights are all connected - take away one, and the value of the others goes down.  He believed these rights should be beyond the power of the government.

Taylor said that in the "state of nature," strong and mean people have more power.  But he wanted this not to be true in a civilized society.  To create a good society, Taylor thought the government must consider both good and bad in people.  He believed that all government actions are good or bad, like people.  He thought good principles are those that protect private property, help farming, and stop selfish business.  A government with good principles would do what is fair, no matter who is in power.  Taylor believed that selfishness is natural, but it is bad when it hurts others.

Taylor wanted a government that is very limited, with only the powers the Constitution says it has.  He thought a big government is expensive and could be mean.  But he also thought that following the Constitution too closely could be bad, without knowing the intentions of the people who made it.  Taylor thought the Declaration of Independence is more important than the Constitution, because it says the United States is a group of independent states, not one country.

We look at Figure 17. The number of people who submit their commuter logs goes down sharply in the third month of the project. This is not good news. It is hard to know why this happens. One reason might be the cold weather in New England. Fewer people walk or bike to school in the winter. Also, December is the end of the school year. Students are busy finishing schoolwork and getting grades. They may forget to fill out the log. The holiday season starts in December and students go home for a month. They do not need to come to school. Classes start again in January. This might be another reason for the low number of logs. We started the Carpool Challenge Week in March. This was a special event to get people excited about the project again. It helped to increase the number of logs in March.

We had another problem. Many people like to drive their cars. This is a big part of our culture. We need to make alternative ways of commuting more attractive. We gave out prizes like gift cards to restaurants and coffee shops. We also gave gift cards to a bookstore and some stores. It would be interesting to know if bigger prizes would help more. For example, we could have given away a bike or a new car. This might have helped people stay interested in the project. The prizes did not change much during the project. If we had announced bigger prizes in December and January, we might have gotten more people to participate.

An ETF is a type of security.  It follows a group of things like an index or a basket of assets.  But it is more flexible and trades like a stock on a stock exchange.  An ETF gives you the safety of a group of investments and the benefits of owning one stock.  You can sell it short, buy with borrowed money, and buy a small amount.  These benefits are attractive.  But there are some problems.  You have to pay a fee to buy or sell an ETF, just like you do to buy a stock.  One good thing about ETFs is that there are many different kinds available.  But it is always a good idea to check if the benefits are real and how big they are.  In this effort, we will look at the ETF IHF and compare it to its top 10 holdings.  We want to see if owning one ETF is as good as owning 10 different stocks.  We will also see if there is a better way to put these stocks together for a better return.

To make this easier, we will only look at the top 10 stocks that make up 63.58% of the ETF.  These are the stocks that make the ETF valuable.  Below are the top 10 stocks and how much of the ETF they make up.

To see how well these 10 stocks represent the ETF, we can use a formula to calculate their Beta and return.  We will use the percentage of the ETF that each stock makes up.  The results are in the chart below.

From the chart, we can see that a portfolio of just the top 10 stocks would be 6.11% higher than the ETF.  This is a 16% increase in returns.  We can also see that the Beta of the top 10 stocks is .12 lower than the ETF.  This means that the top 10 stocks could give a higher return with less risk.  But we need to know if these results are real or just a chance.

To be sure, we will look at how much each stock can change in value.  We will calculate the standard deviation of each stock and compare it to the ETF.  This will help us see if the two portfolios are really different.

One of Edgar Allan Poe's famous poems is called "Dream-Land." In "Dream-Land," Poe uses a word called "Thulé" two times. This word comes from Virgil, a famous ancient writer. Virgil used this word to name a place north of Britain. Many people thought this place was the edge of the known world. Poe liked the work of German writers. 

Poe's use of "Thulé" is important. It shows Poe knew the work of a German writer named Goethe. Goethe wrote a famous play called "Faust." It was published in two parts, the first part in 1808 and the second part in 1832, the year Goethe died. In the second part of "Faust," there is a short poem called "The King of Thulé." This poem is about a king whose wife dies after giving him a special cup. After her death, the king drinks a lot and cries. He then decides it is time to die and leaves his possessions to his children. He throws the cup into the ocean and dies. Poe's poem "Dream-Land" and Goethe's "The King of Thulé" are similar. Maybe one is a dark version of the other. This could be because Poe was thinking about his own loss and his drinking. A man named H P Grattan wrote a play called "Faust" in 1842, a year before Poe used the word "Thulé" in "The Pit and the Pendulum." Poe mentions Thule twice in his writings. He uses the phrase "ultma Thule" in "The Pit and the Pendulum" and "Dream-Land" twice as a book end. "The King of Thule" and "Dream-Land" can be read as two connected poems. In "Dream-Land," the speaker talks about a dark and lonely place called Thule. He sees a world without color and is haunted by dead friends. This is like the story of the king in "The King of Thule," who has lost his wife and is lonely. Goethe was a famous writer that Poe would have known. Poe admired another writer, Tennyson, who liked Goethe's work. Poe would have seen Goethe's work in many books that were published after the original publication.

Under California law, can a person who got hurt after slipping and falling on a spill in a grocery store get extra money as punishment from the store owner? The store owner was told twice about the spill, but he did not clean it up for 30 minutes because he was eating dinner.

A judge is unlikely to quickly stop the case. To get extra money as punishment, the person who got hurt must show that the store owner acted on purpose to cause harm. The store owner must have known that not cleaning the spill could cause an injury. The person who got hurt will argue that the store owner should have known this because many people had slipped and fallen in the store in the past because of spills. The store owner still did not clean up the spill.

The person who got hurt will also argue that the store owner's actions were very bad. However, this argument is not very strong. But it may still be valid because many people had slipped and fallen in the store in 2009, and the store owner did not take steps to make the store safe.

On October 13, 2009, an employee of the grocery store told the manager about a spill in an aisle. The manager said he was on a break and could not deal with customer complaints. Another employee told the manager about the spill 15 minutes later, but he still did not clean it up. At 5:30 pm, the person who got hurt slipped and fell on the spill and got a serious back injury. Before this happened, five other people had slipped and fallen in the store in 2009. The person who got hurt is now suing the grocery store for money to cover her medical expenses and for extra money as punishment.

In California, a person can get extra money as punishment if the other person acted with "oppression, fraud, or malice." Malice is when someone acts on purpose to cause harm. It can also be when someone acts very badly and with a clear disregard for the safety of others. The court has said that this is the case when someone knows that their actions could cause harm and still does not try to stop it.

I studied Islam in a class at CBC about four years ago.  We had a big discussion in class about whether Islam is a hostile religion.  I think this question is still important today.  I have seen how the media's view of Islam has changed since 9/11.  At first, they had a negative view.  Later, they became too friendly.  I don't think in 2001 we could have elected a president like Barack Obama, who comes from a family with Muslim background.

The biography of the Prophet Muhammad is interesting to me.  But it does not match the history I know of Muhammad.  I thought he forced people to become Muslims.  But the biography says he was a kind and humble man.  People came to him because they believed in his teachings.  I also see some similarities between the work of Jesus and the miracles of Muhammad.  For example, Muhammad multiplied food so there was enough for many people.  I think the writers wanted to show Muhammad as a humble man who did not need to prove anything.  It makes me think they are trying to take credit for the life of Jesus.

There are many stories in the biography that sound like they are trying to prove that Muhammad was a good leader.  But these stories come from second-hand information.  I don't think this makes them more believable.  It makes me question the truth of the stories.  I don't like this because it makes the stories seem suspicious.

What bothers me most is that the biography tries to make Muhammad seem like a kind and wise man.  But history says he was not like that.  I think Muslims today should know the real story of Muhammad's life.

The teachings of Jesus and the ideas he believed in are not what many Christians follow today.  If we look at the history of Christianity, we see that it has moved away from its roots.  In the past, people did not think about this.  Today, however, there is a growing awareness that things have changed.  Many people are thinking about what Jesus really said and did.  They want to know the true meaning of his teachings.

Soon, a new movement will start.  People will try to understand what Jesus really meant.  They will look at the ideas that were added to Christianity over time.  This will take a long time, but it will happen.  Christianity will go back to its original form.  People will understand the true meaning of Jesus' teachings.

When this happens, Christianity will become more like it was when Jesus was alive.  People will focus on his ideas, not on the things that were added later.  The church as an organization will still be strong.  But the differences between Christians will fade away.  Instead of being different from each other, they will be more alike.

History is full of examples of big changes.  One example is how the Roman Empire, which once persecuted Christians, became a Christian country.  Our country has also had big changes.  From slavery to freedom, from being against African-Americans to having an African-American president.

A big change is coming in the Christian world.  People will start to see Jesus' words as symbols, not as exact statements.  This will help make the change happen.  To understand what I am saying, we need to look at the history of Christianity.  Before Jesus, there was only Judaism.  The Jewish people had many different ideas and groups.  They had Sadducees, Pharisees, and others.  They did not all agree on what was true.

The Jungle shows how people are naturally selfish. They only think about themselves and want a good life. They do not care about others who are lower than them. The book shows this in many ways. The owners of big factories want to make their companies as big and successful as possible. They do not care about anything that gets in their way or gets hurt because of their success. They do not worry about the pollution their factories make. They also do not care about their workers. They want to make money, not help their employees. The owners force their workers to work long hours for little pay. They can fire many people at once without warning. At that time, there were no laws to protect workers. The owners had too much power.

The book shows that the workers were treated badly. They had no help or organizations to turn to. Some workers tried to form groups to help themselves, but these groups were not very helpful. The workers were treated so badly that they were almost like slaves. They were always hungry and had to work hard to survive. They depended on their bosses for everything.

The Jungle is a sad story about how people are treated in a big city. It shows that some people do not care about others and only want to make more money.

Many authors use special ways to give readers a certain feeling. Some methods are more effective. F. Scott Fitzgerald uses many of these methods in his novel The Great Gatsby. He pairs words together that do not usually fit to give a special feeling. He also uses symbols to give meaning. Fitzgerald uses many colors to give meaning to important things. He builds up the meaning of colors like white, gray, red, and pink. He uses these colors to remind readers of a feeling.

Fitzgerald makes white and gray mean the same thing - uniformity. White is nice and gray is old and faded. He uses these colors in the beginning of the novel. Many characters wear white. Daisy and Jordan wear white clothes. People at parties wear white. Even the streets are white. But Fitzgerald also uses these colors for ordinary things. He makes the city streets "white chasms" and the cars "gray."

Later, Fitzgerald uses white and gray to show that something is not important. He uses these colors to describe Daisy. He says she is wearing white and is like a uniform. This shows that Daisy is not a special person, but just something Gatsby wants. Fitzgerald uses this technique many times to show that Daisy is like a uniform.

Fitzgerald uses colors to remind readers of a feeling. He uses red and pink to show something is important. But that is a different story.

San Diego County is a great place for growing food. The weather is mild and sunny. Many crops grow well here, including tomatoes, citrus fruits, leafy greens, squash, broccoli, and herbs. Many people in San Diego want organic food. They are willing to pay more for it. This is good news for farmers who use special methods that do not hurt the earth.

Some farmers in San Diego give tours of their farms. People can visit and learn about the farms. They can also walk and look for birds. This helps the farmers get money and help the environment.

Organic farming has many benefits. It helps plants and animals live in the area. But it is harder and more expensive than other ways of farming. Farmers must work harder to get rid of pests and weeds. They also need to put special food on the soil to help it grow.

The land I am talking about is near the town of Potrero. It is 160 acres of land with different kinds of plants and trees. Many animals live there, including some that are in danger. The government has a plan to protect them. The plan includes over 100 kinds of plants and animals. Some are endangered, like the kangaroo rat and the California gnatcatcher.

People lived in this area a long time ago. Then, ranchers and loggers came. They used the land for many years. Now, a farmer could use the land for organic farming. I looked at a government program to see how a farmer could get help. I also looked at a real farm in the area to see what they do.

Culture is a very important part of any negotiation. But culture is not the same as what it might seem to be. It is not a single thing. It is not the same everywhere. We should not say that all Russians are stubborn or that all Japanese people are accommodating. This is not true. Understanding a culture is not just about what it is, but also what it means. Knowing about a culture can help us understand how it will affect a negotiation.

When we meet people from another culture, we think of them in relation to our own culture. This can lead to comparisons. To understand another culture, we can learn about its history or its customs. We should not try to change another culture, but accept it for what it is. This is especially true in negotiations, especially if we have less strength or power.

Culture does not only exist between countries. Companies also have their own culture. For example, some companies value hard work and long hours, while others value relaxation and freedom. We can see this in the way employees dress, how they communicate, and how they are hired. Even within the same country, different companies can have different cultures. This shows that cultures are not always what they seem.

Values are even more important to understand. They tell us why a culture behaves in a certain way. If a culture values saving face or harmony, a negotiator will not publicly disagree or argue. If a culture values hard work, a negotiator will not settle easily. Understanding these values can help us prepare for a negotiation. But it is also important to learn about our opponent and their needs to make a successful negotiation.

Two famous thinkers, St. Anselm and Thomas Aquinas, each wrote about the existence of God. We will look at their ideas and see if one is better than the other. We will assume they are both correct about the Christian God.

To compare their ideas, we will first look at St. Anselm's argument. He says we can find God in our own minds. He believes that because we think about God, God must exist. St. Anselm thinks we don't need to look outside ourselves for proof of God's existence. He says this is an example of faith.

Thomas Aquinas has a different idea. He thinks we can prove God exists using reason and what we see in the world. He does not need faith. Aquinas gives five reasons why God exists. He says that change, cause, chance, and order in the world all need a creator. He is saying that God must exist because the world is not perfect and has problems that need a solution.

We can see that their ideas are different. St. Anselm believes in faith, while Thomas Aquinas believes in reason. We will continue to look at their ideas to see if one is better than the other.

A long time ago, in the fifth or sixth century, a prince was born. He would later be called Buddha. This man lived a long life and became very wise. He gave up the world and found enlightenment. His teachings started Buddhism, a very old religion. It is now 2,500 years old. Today, it is different from what it was when Buddha was alive. This change can be seen in many countries, like Sri Lanka. In Sri Lanka, people celebrate the water-cutting ceremony every year. Monks and normal people take part in this ceremony. It has some importance, but Buddha never taught about a celebration like this. Changes like this happen in the Theravada Buddhist community. They occur in both the monastery and the community of regular people. These changes happen because of internal and external forces.

Internal forces come from people who follow the Buddha's teachings. External forces come from people who do not follow Buddhism. A hostile force is something that hurts the Buddhist community. A benign force is something that helps or does not hurt the community.

Let us look at the basics of Theravada Buddhism. Buddhists trust in three things: the Buddha, the Dhamma, and the Sangha. The Dhamma is the Buddhist teachings. They are found in the Tripitaka - three baskets of text. The Sutta Pitaka has the Suttas, the Vinaya Pitaka has the rules for living, and the Abhidhamma Pitaka has the ideas about the world. These ideas are Anatta (no soul), Dukkha (suffering in life), and Anicca (nothing is permanent). Understanding these ideas can end the cycle of death and rebirth, called Sansara. Sansara is a cycle of suffering, desire, hatred, and delusion. When one becomes enlightened, these things go away.

The Vinaya Pitaka has rules for living. For non-monks, there are five rules: do not kill, do not lie, do not steal, do not misbehave, and do not take alcohol. Monks have many more rules. The most important idea in Buddhism is the Four Noble Truths. First, life has suffering. Second, attachment causes suffering. Third, suffering can be overcome.

The United States and Mexico had a long rivalry from 1836 to 1893. This lasted for 57 years. The worst time of this rivalry was the Mexican-American War from 1846 to 1848. The United States won and got new land from Mexico. This included Texas and the American Southwest. The two countries had many problems, but the rivalry finally stopped before the First World War.

This is not unusual. Countries that share a border often have disagreements. These disagreements can lead to long-lasting rivalries. The United States and Mexico are an example of this. Many countries near the United States have good relations with it. However, Mexico and Cuba have had problems with the United States for a long time.

One problem between the two countries was religion. Many people in the United States did not like Catholicism. This was a major issue between the two countries. In the past, the United States and the Soviet Union had a rivalry based on politics. But the United States and Mexico had a rivalry based on religion. This was a problem because of the distrust between the English and Spanish.

Diehl and Goerts wrote about 17 problems between Mexico and the United States during the 57-year rivalry. Most of these problems were about border issues. These issues included border raids from Mexican territory into the United States. The United States and Mexico finally stopped these problems when they used force to control their borders.

The rivalry between the two countries started to end when Mexico became dependent on the United States. The United States then changed its goals from expanding its territory to helping Mexico economically.

Fifteen years ago, I got very sick with an illness I did not know about. I was 46 years old and a nurse. I chose to be a nurse because people always told me, "You can find a job easily because people will always get sick." My dream was to be a scientist or a journalist, but I chose nursing instead.

Now, I am disabled. I have been getting money from the government for 15 years, but I have nothing left. Every day is hard for me. I am lucky to have my family and some good friends who help me. When disaster happens, it is hard to feel strong.

My point is that bad things can happen in life. We cannot always prepare for them and need help from others. I agree that the government is not always reliable. But I think it is better for Americans to help each other and ask for help instead of trying to do everything alone.

Some people say that America was built on individualism. But the pioneers who came to America a long time ago did not make it by themselves. They needed each other's help. So, be prepared for disasters. I have a kit with food, water, and other important things in case of an emergency. But it is also important to know your neighbors and help them.

Why do living things change over time? Are there limits that influence how they change? In 1917, D'Arcy Thompson said that it is hard to explain even simple living things with math. Today, we still face this problem. Recently, scientists have used math to study how some animals grow and develop over time. Our study is exploring how math can help us understand how living things change over time.

We are studying the shell of a certain type of animal called Prunum. We want to know how it changes over time and how it has changed in the past. We used special pictures taken with X-rays to measure the shell's shape. We then used a computer program to create models of what the shell might have looked like in the past. These models help us understand how living things can change.

A shell is like a tube that grows over time. It makes a spiral shape, with each part of the shell growing around a center point. This center point is called the columella. The shell grows in rounds, called whorls. Each whorl is connected by a line, called a suture. The last whorl is the biggest. The shell has a top and a bottom, a point called the apex and a base. The animal lives in its shell through an opening called the aperture.

We can look at a shell from different angles. There are four main views: from the top, from the bottom, from the side, and from the front. The front view is the usual way to look at a shell.

To count the whorls, we look at the shell from the top. We draw a line where the first connection between whorls starts. Then, we count the whorls from that line. We can only count a whole number of whorls. If a whorl is half done, we count it as half.

A shell is like a path that the animal follows as it grows. We can use math to trace this path. We can then change the math to see how the animal's growth might have been different. This helps us understand how living things change over time.

Indonesia's rates of baby and young child deaths have not changed much in the last ten years.  The country is almost on track to meet some of the goals from the Millennium Development Plan, like improving water and sanitation.  However, progress in health care for mothers and babies is slow.  This means Indonesia will likely not meet its goals by 2015.  There are many reasons for this.  We will talk about them below.

One good thing is that more babies are born with a trained health worker present.  Now, 72% of births have a trained worker.  But, even though this is an improvement, it is not as good as it sounds.  Many of these trained workers are midwives who cannot help in case of a problem.  This is why many mothers die from heavy bleeding.  There is still much work to do.

Fewer children are treated by a health worker when they have diarrhea.  We do not have complete information about care for new mothers after birth.  However, it is clear that this is a problem.  Few mothers and babies get the care they need.

Few women have a cesarean section.  This is a problem.  The rate of cesarean sections is 7% in cities, but only 2% in rural areas.  This means that cities have better access to healthcare than rural areas.  This is unfair.

Another problem is that people with less money have a hard time getting healthcare.  In fact, there is a 27% difference in healthcare use between the richest and the poorest people in the country.  The poor cannot afford healthcare because they have to pay out of their own pocket.

Now, we must think about how to improve healthcare for mothers and babies.  The main question is how to make healthcare services more available.  Should we make programs to help mothers and babies, or should we make the healthcare system better in general?  There are pros and cons to each approach.  Program-specific approaches are attractive because they are clear and can give quick results.  However, this can lead to problems.  When we spend a lot of money on one area, it can leave other areas without enough money.  Also, many programs can cause confusion and extra work for the healthcare system.

Victorian novels are noted for their detailed descriptions and focus on the rich people of that time. Two famous novels that are different from this type are "Oliver Twist" and "Wuthering Heights". These novels often use mystery and strange events to help readers understand the characters. This makes the characters more interesting and adds depth to their thoughts and feelings.

In "Oliver Twist", the main character has many strange and confusing thoughts. He is still seeing two men, Sikes and Crackit, arguing. The words they say are still in his mind. When he pays attention, he finds that he is talking to them. Suddenly, he hears the sound of guns and there are loud cries and shouts. He feels pain and is moved quickly away. He sees many strange things, but he is not in control.

In "Oliver Twist", the author uses strange events, like dreams, to show what is happening inside the main character's mind. In one scene, Oliver remembers a violent event that happened to him. He relives it as if it is happening again. He is very scared and in pain. He does not understand what is happening to him. The author wants the reader to see that Oliver has no control over his life. He is not in charge of what happens to him. The author wants the reader to feel sorry for Oliver.

In another scene, the main character says that time is passing quickly. A day comes and goes, and then night comes again. But it is not a normal day and night. The day is short and the night is long. The main character is very unhappy. He is in a difficult situation and it is hard for him to feel safe.

A few years ago, I worked in an after-school program that helped elementary school students. I tried my best to help them in their difficult subjects, but I was good at English and reading. My boss asked me to help a boy named Adrian. He was in third or fourth grade and had trouble reading. I saw that something was strange. He knew some letters, but others he did not understand. He spoke good English, but his mother did not speak English. She spoke Spanish.

One day, I took care of him while his classmates went on a trip. His mother came in and we talked in Spanish, but I did not know much Spanish. I then understood that Adrian could read, but did not know the English alphabet. I hope he is doing better now.

I tell this story to show that a language problem exists in schools, especially in California. Even if a child speaks good English, reading can be hard. I think everyone agrees that this is a problem. The solution for Adrian was simple: tutoring in English reading. But for children who do not speak much English, the problem is more complicated.

There is no one answer. We need to use many things together. We can use the dual language system, mainstream immersion, private tutors, and ESL classes. But we must use them all together. 

The dual language system is a good idea. It helps all children, not just those who speak Spanish. Children in this kind of program do better in school. Many people are afraid of this idea, thinking it is a waste of money and that most children will not benefit. But this is not true. If we use this system in all schools, all children will benefit.

But how do we do this? Do we need all teachers to be bilingual? No, that is not possible. We can have special helpers who are bilingual. They can assist teachers and students. This is a good idea.

When we are young, people often tell us that there is something bigger than we are. This is something we cannot understand. Some people go to church to learn about it. Others go to the temple or look inside themselves for answers. Many people accept the religion their parents teach them. But some people do not believe in it. They think there is nothing beyond what they know. They may accept one idea and then change their mind and accept another. We search for meaning in life through our own ideas about spirituality.

I asked my father about his favorite bird. It was a cardinal. We sat on our porch, listening to the rain. He looked out into the rain, thinking about something. He had lost weight and his hair was thinning. He did not look at me. I felt sad, scared, and could not talk to him about how much I would miss him. I hugged him and we sat together in the rain.

My father died in December, a few days after my twenty-second birthday. The medicine and radiation did not help him. They kept him alive a little longer. I wanted to remember my father when he was alive, not how he died. I did not want to see him go away. I wanted to remember him as he was, not how he suffered. I thought, "What kind of God would do this?" I did not pray to God that night. If God exists, I thought, he is not listening to me.

I did not want to watch my father die. I wanted to remember him, not how he died. I knew my father better than anyone. I knew he would not want me to watch him die. So I stayed in bed for three days, waiting for the news.

No one called me.

The Gothic Novel is an interesting mix of old and new. This is exactly how writer Ian Watt describes it. The Gothic style has been both praised and criticized. Some people say it is shallow, while others say it evokes a feeling of the 'terrible sublime' (Burke). The first Gothic Novel, Horace Walpole's The Castle of Otranto, combined old and new ideas to create a new way to write stories. Walpole used old theatrical elements and new ideas to create what he called "A Gothic Story" (Walpole 4). The Gothic style uses ideas from medieval theater, architecture, and traditions. Even when The Castle of Otranto was first published, the word "gothic" was used to describe many things. Some people thought it was old-fashioned or not sophisticated.

The combination of the old and new ideas in Gothic novels is what makes them interesting. This is because the old ideas are presented in a new way, allowing readers to see the characters' feelings and thoughts more clearly. This is why Gothic novels have been popular for a long time, even though they were written a long time ago.

One important idea in Gothic novels is the concept of chivalry. Chivalry was a way to train knights in the Middle Ages. It meant being brave, honorable, and competent. Many Gothic writers, including Walpole, liked chivalry because it represented a high ideal. They thought that people in their time did not live up to this ideal. They used chivalric ideas and manners to make the past seem romantic and ideal. This is because Walpole and others wanted to show that people in the past were better than those in the present.

Walpole wrote The Castle of Otranto during a difficult time in history. He was worried about the future and thought that people had lost the good qualities of the past. This is why he wrote about characters like Frederic, who was a prince and a brave and courteous knight. Frederic's description includes many traditional chivalric images. He has suffered a great deal and is now supposed to be dead. But he is actually alive and will return to fight for what is right. The idea of the gallant and courteous knight is an important part of the Gothic style.

The supply chain is a series of actions that helps move goods from the customer's order to the final product. It includes getting raw materials, making the product, and delivering it to the customer. The term supply chain management was created in 1982 by a consultant named Keith Oliver. He explained how to plan and control the supply chain to meet customer needs quickly and efficiently.

There are six important parts of a supply chain: making the product, getting the materials, inventory, location, transportation, and information. Business managers use these parts to give the best service to customers.

First, making the product is the start of the supply chain. Making the product is the base for the whole supply chain. The making stage answers the questions of when, why, where, and how things are made. Before making the product, managers must know what customers want. They look at the market to see what customers need. The market shows what customers are asking for.

After studying the market, managers decide what products to make and how many. Then they decide where to make the products and which factory will make the right amount of products for the customers. Managers also decide how to schedule work and take care of the machines. Making the product is very important in the supply chain. Every detail is crucial. If managers do not plan carefully, it can take a long time and cost a lot of money.

For example, I used to work at Wal-Mart and Target. Both companies have a plan for each part of the business. There is a plan for how employees dress and how goods are received from trucks. Having a plan helps the company work smoothly and avoid confusion.

The second important part of the supply chain is getting the materials. Getting the materials means making decisions about the company's strengths and weaknesses. A company may have many different departments that make different parts of a product. The manager decides which department is best for each part. The manager may also decide to ask another company to help make the product. This is called outsourcing. The main reason for outsourcing is to make the product quickly and with good quality while keeping costs low.

A sign on a street in Burma, also known as Myanmar, says Hitler is alive. Ellen Page, a famous actress, holds a cardboard sign with this message. Burma is a country in Southeast Asia. It is ruled by a group of military leaders who took control in 1962. In 2007, people protested in the streets. These protests were called the Saffron Revolution. Many Buddhist monks led the protests. They wore yellow robes. The government allowed the monks to protest at first, but then violence increased. The military attacked the monasteries. They arrested and imprisoned journalists. A Japanese journalist was killed in 2007. The government says 13 people were killed, but a former army officer claims many more were killed.

This is not new. Governments have wanted to control their people for a long time. In ancient Rome, leaders thought they were chosen by gods. Japanese leaders think they are gods. Our current president has meetings with a man who says he represents a group called Stupid People Worldwide.

There are many examples of governments hurting their people. In 1989, people protested in China's Tiananmen Square. Many were killed. The number of deaths is not known. In Rwanda, a group of people killed others because of their tribe. Many people were hurt or killed. In Germany, a man named Hitler hurt many people because of their religion.

Duke Ellington's place in jazz comes from his long life and his ability to make his orchestra strong. Ellington did not often play the piano in his songs, but as a composer, he wrote great music that showed how well his band members could play. He made a framework where musicians could improvise and also wrote music that used the special sound of each musician. This made his songs sound new and original.

The Grove Music dictionary says Ellington's sound was special because he used the voice as an instrument. This is seen in Creole Love Call, a song he made early in his career. In this song, Ellington uses the voice to add color and texture without words. He also uses the voice to fit with the style of each musician. This song is a slow blues with six parts. Each part is different. 

- Part 1: A call and response between voice and wind instruments. The voice starts smooth, then gets rougher.
- Part 2: A muted trumpet solo that makes the basic melody sound longer and uses some extra notes.
- Part 3: A clarinet solo that sounds high and is backed by a piano that plays in a special rhythm.
- Part 4: The whole band plays a call and response, just like in part 1, but with brass and wind instruments.
- Part 5: The most exciting part of the song, where the wind instruments call and respond in a high sound, and the brass and rhythm instruments play in a special way.
- Part 6: The song goes back to the start, with call and response between voice and wind instruments. This time, the voice sounds like a special instrument.

Ellington used the voice to make his songs sound new and interesting. In Hot and Bothered, he combined his good orchestration with his ear for sound. He used a call and response between a trumpeter and a singer to make a rich and special sound. It Don't Mean a Thing (If It Ain't Got That Swing) shows how well he used a trombone player to introduce the melody.

Ellington's use of the voice in his songs is one way he made jazz special. He made his musicians sound good and created new and interesting music.

She felt something was missing in her life. This feeling did not go away. It started when she was 14 years old. It was still there three years later, when she was 17. She wanted a person, not just a thing. But she did not like any boys. Some boys liked her. They tried to talk to her, but she did not like them. She often thought about why this was happening to her.

She lived at home with her parents. They were kind and calm. They rarely argued with each other. They argued with her only about her independence. She was different from her parents. She was outgoing and fun, and everyone liked her.

Today was not a calm day. She heard a loud sound from the kitchen. She ran to the room and saw her mother on the floor. Her mother was in pain and saying "Ow" many times. Her daughter ran to her and put her hand on her. "Mom, what's wrong?!" she asked. Her mother said, "Ow... sweetie, I need you to take me to the hospital." Her daughter helped her mother to the car and drove her to the hospital.

The hospital had a bad smell. But she was not thinking about that. She was thinking about her mother. She carried her mother into the hospital and called the doctors for help. Some people came and helped her mother. They put her on a special bed and took her to see a doctor.

Her mother fell from a stool while getting a vase from a high cabinet.

This study had one purpose. It was to show that eating a Mediterranean-style diet, called the Med diet, can help prevent heart disease and stroke. We found that women who ate this type of food had a lower risk of these diseases.

The Med diet is a special way of eating. It includes more plant foods like fruits, nuts, whole grains, and legumes. It also includes fish and less animal products and fatty foods. Drinking some alcohol in moderation is okay.

Before this study, other studies had shown that eating a Med diet can help lower the risk of dying from any cause and from heart disease. But they did not look at the risk of stroke or dying from a stroke.

We studied 74,886 women between the ages of 38 and 63 who were not sick with heart disease or diabetes. They were all part of a big study of nurses in 11 US states. We asked them to tell us about what they ate over the past year six times between 1984 and 2004. More than 95% of the women kept participating for 20 years.

We used questionnaires to ask about what they ate. We also checked to make sure the information was correct. We looked at the women's medical records to see if they got sick with heart disease, died from heart disease, or had a stroke. If we did not have the records, we considered it a possible case and included it in our study.

We also looked at other things like how much they weighed, if they smoked, if they took aspirin, if they took vitamins, and if they exercised. We took the average of what they ate over the past two years to get a better idea of their long-term eating habits. We controlled for things that could affect the results, like age, smoking, weight, menopause, and exercise.

We used a special method to see if eating a Med diet was linked to heart disease and stroke. We looked at the women who ate the most Med-style food and compared them to those who ate the least. We found that women who ate more Med-style food had a lower risk of heart disease and stroke.

Over 20 years, we found 2391 cases of heart disease, 1763 cases of stroke, and 1077 deaths from heart disease and stroke. Women who ate the most Med-style food were less likely to get heart disease or stroke than women who ate the least. Their risk was 29% lower.

In 2007, the United States had a big financial problem. Many people lost their jobs, and the value of homes dropped. The government and big companies were in trouble. We must ask: how did this happen? And how can we stop it? In short, the financial problem was caused by bad choices made by politicians. They forced banks to give money to people who could not pay it back. The banks also sold these loans to other companies, which created a big problem.

The financial crisis started in 1999. President Clinton wanted to be president again. He wanted to be popular, so he made it easier for people to get loans. This created a big problem for the future. A writer from the New York Times, Steven Holmes, wrote about this in 1999. He said Fannie Mae, a company that gives loans, was under pressure to give loans to people who could not afford them. He also said this could cause a problem in the future.

Many things combined to make the economy worse. New types of loans were made, like loans with rates that could change. These loans made it easy for people to borrow money, but it also made them very vulnerable. When the housing market dropped, many people lost a lot of money. The top five investment banks in the US had $4.1 trillion dollars of debt in 2007. This was a big problem. Some banks were sold or shut down, and others were forced to change.

Fannie Mae and Freddie Mac, two big companies that help people get loans, had $5 trillion dollars of debt. They were put under government control in 2008. This financial crisis was a big problem that affected many people.

Exposition is a part of your story where you tell the reader important information. But it can also be boring. Dr. Merlin says she sometimes gets frustrated when she writes too much and her readers lose interest.

You probably know the writing tip "Show, don't tell." But Dr. Merlin still makes mistakes and writes too much exposition. This is when you tell the reader too much information at once. It can be like a character dumping too much information on another character.

Exposition is like a big speech. The author is telling the reader what to know. In stories, this can be when one character talks a lot about something. In film, it's when someone talks a lot to another character.

Let's look at an example. A story might say, "The heroine met her husband at a place and time. They got married in a big ceremony. He was murdered in front of her." But if the story spends two pages on this, with only a few lines of dialogue, it's boring. You want to know more about the husband and why he's important to the heroine.

You should show the reader how much the husband loves his wife and how she feels about him. Maybe he says something kind or does something special. Maybe she thinks about him often or feels sad when he's not there. This helps the reader connect with the story and care about what happens.

In short, you need to add details to the story. You can't just say, "They met, they married, he died." You need to show the reader why this is important. 

Sometimes it's hard to resist telling too much. Maybe you're introducing a new character and you want to tell everything about him. But try to show it instead. For example, you might say, "He used to be in the Air Force and now he works at a gas station. He likes fishing and dreams of owning the station one day." This is better than saying, "He was in the Air Force, now he works at a gas station, he's been married twice, no kids, likes to fish, and wants to own the station."

I watched two news programs from Columbus, Ohio. The first one was live from NBC 4 on August 13, 2011. The main story was about a man in Ashley, Ohio. He stabbed his wife. The police arrested him. His name was Shad Hostettler. The news showed his picture. He looked very bad. They talked about this story for two minutes. I think they said enough.

The next story was about a man named Travis Buyers, 18 years old. He was shot in the Sharon Woods area. He was very sick. The police did not know who shot him. They were investigating. This story was short. I think it was because the man was black. I have seen this before. When a white person is a victim of a crime, the news talks a lot. But when a black person is a victim, the news talks less.

The next story was about a helicopter that was shot. It was a Med-Flight helicopter. The police think it was a .22 caliber bullet from a rifle. They want people to help find the person who shot the helicopter. They are offering a reward of $5,000.

The news also talked about the weather. They said it would rain and be hot on Saturday afternoon. The temperature would be in the mid to low eighties all weekend. They wanted to keep people watching.

Another story was about a robbery at a store in Columbus. A black man robbed the store. He was wearing a hoodie and was about 6 feet tall and 150 pounds. The news talked a lot about how black he was.

The last story was about a man named Rene Rodriguez. He was a big drug dealer from Texas. He was caught for selling a lot of marijuana in Ohio. He was sentenced to 25 years in prison. The news said he would be in prison for 300 months. They also said he was Hispanic. I don't think that was important to the story.

There is a strong connection between brothers. This connection can be very good or very bad. It is made up of many feelings: love, pride, jealousy, and anger. Brothers know each other very well. They can see themselves in each other. When brothers are very sad or in big trouble, their true feelings are shown. These feelings can have big costs. To understand brothers, you must understand the problems that come with their feelings. When you can look at a brother and see yourself, you see yourself in a real way.

In a story called "The Scarlet Ibis", two brothers deal with these feelings. They go on a hard journey in a beautiful place. They are very disappointed and very proud at the same time. Only one brother survives. The story shows how one brother feels through how he acts and what he does. The narrator also tells us how the brother feels and what he sees in the world around him. This helps us understand why he does the things he does.

The big feeling that drives the brother is pride. From the time he and his little brother Doodle go out together, the brother feels angry at Doodle. He wanted a brother who could do things with him, like running and climbing trees. But Doodle was sick and could not do these things. This was hard for the brother to accept. He even thought about hurting Doodle. But when Doodle smiled, the brother's anger went away. This shows that the brother truly loved his brother.

The human brain is a very complex system. It helps us think and remember. A long time ago, people thought of the brain like a clay tablet. Then they thought of it like a piece of paper. Next, it was like a book. Now, some people think of it like a computer. These ideas are not perfect. They can lead to mistakes.

Information gets into the brain from our senses. Our senses include our eyes, ears, nose, tongue, and skin. They turn things like touch, heat, and light into electrical signals. The brain uses these signals to understand the world.

The brain works in two ways. Bottom-up means breaking down information into small parts. Top-down means using what we already know to help us understand. For example, when you see a picture of a black box, the brain first looks at the colors and edges. Then it uses what it knows about boxes to decide what it is.

The brain also has a filter. It decides what information is important and what we should pay attention to. We might see many things, but we only pay attention to some of them. Our brain can pick out our name in a loud room, but we might not notice every small thing around us.

The brain needs a place to store information. It has three kinds of memory: sensory, working, and long-term. First, information is stored. There are different ways to store different kinds of information. For example, our brains store words in different ways, like how they look, how they sound, and what they mean.

Information is not just stored, it must also be kept safe. Some studies on animals show that the brain keeps information in working memory for about 20 seconds by sending an electrical signal through a group of brain cells. Long-term memory is thought to be stored in the shape of certain kinds of proteins.

There are many ways to think about how the brain stores knowledge. Some come from people's memories, some from computers, and some from studying how the brain works. One idea is that the brain is like a network of connected ideas. For example, if we think of a chair, we might also think of a table, which we might think of as made of wood.

Aldous Huxley is worried about the future. He writes a book called Brave New World to show how people might live in a world controlled by technology and capitalism. In this world, people care more about being happy now than about being an individual. From a young age, they are taught to be happy and not to think deeply. The people in this world are not really in charge. They are controlled by the World Controller. 

We can see that Huxley does not like this kind of society. He uses ideas from Marxism to show his worries. Marxism is a way of thinking about how societies work. Huxley uses words from Marxism, like "homogeny" and "reification", to show that he is worried about the way people live in his world. 

In Brave New World, people do not know about the real world. They are too busy looking after themselves. They are not allowed to think about their place in society. They are happy to buy things and enjoy themselves. The people in charge, the Alphas and Betas, do not care about fairness. They are happy to take what they want. 

In Brave New World, people do not love each other. They do not feel strong emotions. They just want to be happy. They talk about each other's bodies, not their feelings. This shows that Huxley thinks that technology and capitalism are taking away people's freedom to feel and think deeply. 

The people in Brave New World are happy to obey the rules. They do not want to change the way things are. This is like what Marx said about the proletariat, the working class. They are fooled into thinking they are better than others as long as they keep buying and following the rules.

I have been a student at University Park for about two and a half years. Getting around campus can be difficult. My freshman year, I lived in East Halls dorm, which is far from the center of campus. It took me 25 minutes to walk to classes in the Willard building on bad days. The weather in State College can be bad.

I talked to an old friend who rides a bike. He said it is the best way to get around campus. Bicycling is good for your body and is the most efficient way to travel. You can eat a bowl of oatmeal and ride your bike 30 miles or more. I now live off campus, far from the center of campus. I bought a bike this year, and it was a good decision. My classes are in the Thomas building, which is 25 minutes away on foot. But on a bike, it takes only 5 minutes. The road I take, Pollock Road, is not always easy to ride on.

Walking is also a good option, but I am too busy to walk. If I didn't have a bike, I would have to walk to Thomas building every day. That would take 30-40 minutes. That is 2.5 hours every week. I don't have that much time.
